  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/245429.htm", 
  "description": "<p>如果你刚刚花了$299美金购买了上周五才发布的Lumia 1020智能手机，但是没几分钟就被盗，请问你的心情会是如何？随着智能手机盗窃案件的日益猖獗，这种情况并不是不会发生在你的身上。<strong>旧金山地方检察官乔治·加斯科因(George Gascó），正在努力协助领导各大智能手机软硬件制造商，带来使被盗的手机\"不可用\"的功能。</strong>Techhive.com本周报道过，苹果和三星向Gascó展示了它们的放到措施。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ef18cad/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245429.htm&amp;t=%E6%97%A7%E9%87%91%E5%B1%B1%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E6%A3%80%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%98%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%8E%82%E5%95%86%E5%8A%AA%E5%8A%9B%E6%94%B9%E8%BF%9B%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E9%98%B2%E7%9B%97%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245429.htm&amp;t=%E6%97%A7%E9%87%91%E5%B1%B1%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E6%A3%80%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%98%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%8E%82%E5%95%86%E5%8A%AA%E5%8A%9B%E6%94%B9%E8%BF%9B%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E9%98%B2%E7%9B%97%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245429.htm&amp;t=%E6%97%A7%E9%87%91%E5%B1%B1%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E6%A3%80%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%98%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%8E%82%E5%95%86%E5%8A%AA%E5%8A%9B%E6%94%B9%E8%BF%9B%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E9%98%B2%E7%9B%97%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245429.htm&amp;t=%E6%97%A7%E9%87%91%E5%B1%B1%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E6%A3%80%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%98%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%8E%82%E5%95%86%E5%8A%AA%E5%8A%9B