  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/245428.htm", 
  "description": "<p>西数在在6月初的Computex 2013大展上发布了7mm厚度的蓝盘，其最大容量可以达到1TB，<strong>在这个容量上，西数做到了全球最薄，同样在这个厚度上，西数做到了容量最大。</strong>该硬盘采用的是单碟500GB技术（双碟装），<strong>转速为5400RPM，缓存容量为16MB，官方宣称的最快读取速度为140MB/s</strong>，工作中的功耗为1.7W，待机功耗为0.75W，休眠状态下的功耗为0.18W，噪音只有20dB左右。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ef18cac/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245428.htm&amp;t=%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%847mm%E6%9C%BA%E6%A2%B0%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E5%BC%80%E5%8D%96\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245428.htm&amp;t=%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%847mm%E6%9C%BA%E6%A2%B0%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E5%BC%80%E5%8D%96\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245428.htm&amp;t=%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%847mm%E6%9C%BA%E6%A2%B0%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E5%BC%80%E5%8D%96\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245428.htm&amp;t=%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%847mm%E6%9C%BA%E6%A2%B0%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E5%BC%80%E5%8D%96\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245428.htm&amp;t=%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%847mm%E6%9C%BA%E6%A2%B0%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E5%BC%80%E5%8D%96\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http