  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/245427.htm", 
  "description": "<p>最近天气比较热，手机质量安全问题也随之频发，苹果和三星这两大巨头均不止一次中枪。<strong>本月中旬，一名瑞士的18岁女孩使用的三星Galaxy S3电池因不明原因爆炸，导致她的大腿三度灼伤。事故发生以后，三星瑞士分公司已经将手机送回韩国总公司检验，进一步厘清事发原因。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ef18cab/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245427.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E5%9B%9E%E5%BA%94Galaxy+S3%E7%94%B5%E6%B1%A0%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%EF%BC%9A%E9%9D%9E%E5%8E%9F%E8%A3%85%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245427.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E5%9B%9E%E5%BA%94Galaxy+S3%E7%94%B5%E6%B1%A0%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%EF%BC%9A%E9%9D%9E%E5%8E%9F%E8%A3%85%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245427.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E5%9B%9E%E5%BA%94Galaxy+S3%E7%94%B5%E6%B1%A0%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%EF%BC%9A%E9%9D%9E%E5%8E%9F%E8%A3%85%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245427.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E5%9B%9E%E5%BA%94Galaxy+S3%E7%94%B5%E6%B1%A0%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%EF%BC%9A%E9%9D%9E%E5%8E%9F%E8%A3%85%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245427.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E5%9B%9E%E5%BA%94Galaxy+S3%E7%94%B5%E6%B1%A0%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%EF%BC%9A%E9%9D%9E%E5%8